    <title>This is the first smart lock to support ultra wideband </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/O93nhug-No7yLp5EiHyPfCl6xhY=/0x171:1024x854/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583752/World_s_First_Smart_Deadbolt_With_UWB_NFC_Technology.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Ultraloq Bolt Mission UWB Plus NFC is the first smart lock to launch that leverages ultra wideband auto-unlocking technology.&lt;/em&gt; | Image: U-tec&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="AIOm12"&gt;U-tec’s new smart lock will allow your door to unlock automatically as you approach it using ultra wideband (UWB) technology. While U-tec and other lock makers currently have auto-unlock methods that use a &lt;a href="https://support.shopyalehome.com/en_us/how-does-auto-unlock-work-r1tW8RQyD"&gt;combination of BLE, Wi-Fi, and GPS&lt;/a&gt;, these can be unreliable and slow. The &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fu-tec.com%2Fblogs%2Fnews%2Fthe-worlds-first-uwb-technology-in-smart-lock-application-to-surprise-aiot-market&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F13%2F24243694%2Fultraloq-bolt-mission-uwb-matter-smart-lock-apple-home" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Ultraloq Bolt Mission UWB Plus NFC&lt;/a&gt; is the first smart lock to leverage UWB, which promises a simpler, faster, and more reliable experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="BmOAah"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"Apple announces hands-free unlocking for smart locks&amp;amp;nbsp;","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24172054/apple-home-homekit-robot-vacuum-support-smart-locks-wwdc24"},{"title":"You’ll need a new smart lock if you want Apple Home to ‘magically’ unlock your door","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/19/24180813/apple-home-hands-free-unlock-smart-lock-uwb-wwdc-2024"},{"title":"Aliro could unlock a new future for smart locks and digital keys ","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/9/23952637/csa-aliro-new-standard-smart-locks-digital-access"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="WsvcG7"&gt;In addition to UWB, the new lock works over Wi-Fi and Matter and can be unlocked with NFC. At launch, it will work with Android NFC-enabled phones, and U-tec says support for Apple’s Home Key tap-to-open feature will come &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/8/23753915/matter-smart-lock-aqara-u100-apple-home-key"&gt;once it’s available through Matter&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="uhfSyC"&gt;If you don’t want to use any of these newfangled methods of entry,...&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;
    &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243694/ultraloq-bolt-mission-uwb-matter-smart-lock-apple-home"&gt;Continue reading&amp;hellip;&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;

</content>
