    <title>Keurig caught making ‘inaccurate’ recycling claims about its coffee pods     </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="Keurig" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JUKChEWF3aubRXzthrGSTCL1X94=/0x1:5194x3464/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583734/2154292697.0.jpg" /&gt;
